      <title>季风影响电力需求 印度液化天然气进口量将大幅下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/india-s-lng-imports-set-to-slump-as-monsoon-hits-power-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于季风降雨导致天气转冷，电力需求减少，且水力发电增加，挤占了昂贵的燃气发电机，印度蓬勃发展的液化天然气进口量可能会放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/india-s-lng-imports-set-to-slump-as-monsoon-hits-power-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 09:42:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
